descriptionHtml:
This is my Miyuki\'s savegame at Alvar\'s house (chosen to follow Imperials), lvl 1, no quests done, warrior guardian stone chosen (intended to be bow/daggers user).

[b]Mods you need to get same looks:[/b][list]
[*] [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=8583]The Ashen - Oriental Beauty Race by Seren4XX and RadioRagae[/url] (plus hotfixes)
[*] [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=515]More Freckles by Zhoken[/url] (chose smaller file)
[*] [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10357]ApachiiSkyHair Retexture by Bloodysunday[/url]
[*] [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9249]Expanded Color Selection - Eyes by missjennabee[/url][/list]

[b]Mods I use and recommend to use with savegame:[/b][list]
[*] [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666]Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE- by Caliente[/url] (Slim Body)
[*] [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6554]CBBE skin texture V2 V3 plus Thepal and UNP compatible by navetsea[/url]
[*] [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3654]Killer Keos Skimpy CBBE V2 Armor Set -Work In Progress- by Killer Keo[/url]
[*] Airy Ears (google for them or PM me)
[*] [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6515]Invisible Helmets - Aesthetics for Skyrim by DarkenDE[/url]
or better option to use with Airy Ears
[*] [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2460]No Helmets Required by ClassicalNoodle[/url][/list]

I didn\'t forgot anything... I think :P
author: Lestatt Gaara
